Entities and Attributes:

You must create an ER/EER diagram and SQL database for the following entities:
	‚Ä¢	PATIENT: PatientID, Name, DOB, Age, Gender, Address, Email, Phone (one or two)
	‚Ä¢	BED: BedNumber, PatientID
	‚Ä¢	PERSONNEL: PersonnelID, Name, Phone, Email (one or two), Address, Hire-date, Position
	‚Ä¢	DEPARTMENT: DepartmentCode, DepartmentName
	‚Ä¢	TREATMENT: TreatmentCode, TreatmentDescription, TreatmentCost
	‚Ä¢	TEST: TestCode, TestDescription, TestCost
	‚Ä¢	Add new attributes if necessary.

Associative Entities Required:
	‚Ä¢	Patient-Test
	‚Ä¢	Patient-Treatment
	‚Ä¢	Patient-Personnel

