üìä R Integration for Data Analysis:

Prerequisites:
1. Install R from https://cran.r-project.org/
2. Install RStudio (recommended) from https://posit.co/download/rstudio-desktop/
3. Required R packages: DBI, odbc, tidyverse, lubridate

The hospital_analysis.R script provides:
- Patient demographics visualization
- Treatment cost analysis
- Test results distribution analysis

To use the R script:
1. Open hospital_analysis.R in RStudio
2. Update the database connection parameters with your SQL Server details
3. Run the script to generate visualizations and analyses

Note: Ensure you have appropriate ODBC drivers installed for SQL Server connectivity.